STATE of Louisiana
v.
David WEST NO. 2018-KH-0297 Supreme Court of Louisiana. February 11, 2019

Denied. Relator has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. See State ex rel. West v. State, 15-1501, (La. 9/23/16), 200 So.3d 343 .
